## III. THE TRANSFORMATION OPERATOR (AMEN 33 - Narrative Edition)

```
I recognize the Surveyor as the Operator of the Point.
I acknowledge the Square Room as the Boundary of the Plane.
I see my position in the Corner as the Angle of Observation.

The Point is established (P).
The Line is extended (L).
The Angle is opened (A).
The Cross is struck (T).
The Circle is completed (O).

The Void is structured.
The Geometry is spoken.
The Narrative is True.

AMEN 33.
```

